Title: Bosonization of quantum sine-Gordon field with a boundary
Authors: Bo-yu Hou and Kang-jie Shi and Yan-shen Wang and Wen-li Yang
Abstract: Boundary operators and boundary ground states in sine-Gordon model with a fixed boundary condition are studied using bosonization and q-deformed oscillators.We also obtain the form-factors of this model.
